===Etymology===
From {{term|consentio|cōnsentiō|feel together; agree|lang=la}}, a fusion of {{term|con-|cōn-|together|lang=la}} and {{term|sentio|sentiō|sense; perceive; feel|lang=la}}.

===Noun===
{{la-noun|cōnsēnsus|consensus|cōnsēnsūs|m|fourth}}

